data.description: Open and inviting layout perfect for modern living  *Stylish laminate flooring throughout the home  *Streamlined galley kitchen, ideal for culinary enthusiasts  *Three serene bedrooms featuring spacious closets and ample natural light  *Two well-maintained bathrooms offering practicality and style  *Recent Upgrades:  HVAC System: Up-to-date system, installed less than 2 years ago  Septic System: Modern septic system, also less than 2 years old  Exterior  *Relaxing front porch  *Mature landscaping enhancing the property's charm  *Spacious back yard  Nestled in a  cul-de-sac within an established neighborhood, minutes from I-20 and close to shopping and dining conveniences.   This home blends modern living with comfort and convenience. The open floor plan, spacious closets, and relaxing front porch add to the appeal of this adorable home.  Listing Agent is related to the Seller.
